Special Feature:
1. When the user input text, the scroll bar will move automatically.
2. Gradient color in text and Background
3. The user can distinguish themself with other users through the different text color and name color
4. If the user doesn't generate the username, the server will generate a id for you automatically.
5. When the user input the same name as the name in the chatroom. It will be considered as other user.
6. The text will post instantly once after the user key in 
